subject: Hitler; Prayer; Moscow, Idaho; Blitzkrieg

title: Peace of Mind
creator: Psychiana, Inc.

title: Death to the Axis

subject: Hitler; Mussolini; Hirohito; Axis; World War

title: Tack this up in your kitchen

subject: Spirit of God; Psychiana Affirmations; Hitler; Mussolini

title: Marilyn Allen's Challenge
creator: Allen, Marilyn R.
description: Advertisement depicts a man in a suit holding bags of money and a challenge to those that that think God and Right can bring Hitler to his knees. Also includes a letter about Psychiana's need for money in a campaign called ''Blitzkrieg' for God.' Includes a 'Blitzkrieg Campaign' button pin with an illustration of Hitler.
subject: Donations; Blitzkrieg; Hitler; Success; World War; Illustrations

title: It Took the Manifestation of Adolf Hitler
